            is_coffee_table(table) and inside(table, home_office)
        # Select the coffee table within the home office

        if exists cat: item : is_cat(cat) and inside(cat, home_office):
            # If we have already found the cat in the home office, we can directly bring it to the t
able
            bind cat: item where:
                is_cat(cat) and inside(cat, home_office)
            bring_cat_to_table(cat, table)

        else:
            # Check all potential locations in the home office for the cat
            foreach room: item:
                if is_home_office(room) and not visited(room):
                    observe(room, "Check is there the cat in the home office")
